msgstr ":guilabel:`颜色`：如果需要，用户可以选择一种颜色添加到仪表板上的调查行，以增加组织性。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys.rst-1
msgid ""
"The three-dot drop-down menu of options that appears on the Odoo Surveys "
