msgstr "点击打开筛选器选项的第二个下拉菜单后，会出现另外两个选项：:guilabel:`仅限通过` 和 :guilabel:`仅限不通过`。"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/surveys/analysis.rst-1
msgid ""
"The 'Passed and Failed' drop-down menu on the 'See results' page of the Odoo"
